---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro'
---

<Layout
  title="🏆 Featured Sponsors - Manuel Gil - Software Developer & Open Source Advocate"
  description="A huge thank you to those who support my work! Your contributions make a difference. 🙌"
  keywords="sponsors, open source, developer, innovation"
>
  <main class="container mx-auto px-4 pt-20">
    <section class="flex items-center justify-center py-28">
      <div class="max-w-3xl text-center">
        <h1
          class="mb-6 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-accent bg-clip-text text-6xl font-bold text-transparent"
        >
          Sponsors
        </h1>
        <p class="mb-8 text-xl text-zinc-400">
          A huge thank you to those who support my work! Your contributions make a difference. 🙌
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mx-auto mb-16 max-w-3xl">
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <h2 class="mb-6 text-4xl font-bold">🎖 Sponsorship Tiers</h2>
        <p class="mb-6 text-zinc-400">
          Below are the amazing sponsors who help keep open-source projects alive. Each tier comes
          with unique benefits!
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mx-auto mb-16 max-w-3xl">
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <h3 class="mb-6 text-3xl font-bold">🥉 Basic Sponsor</h3>
        <ul class="mb-6 space-y-2 text-zinc-400">
          <li>
            <span class="mr-2 text-primary">▹</span>
            <a
              href="https://github.com/sebasttti"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class="text-primary">Juan Sebastian Joya R.</a
            >
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="mr-2 text-primary">▹</span>
            <a
              href="https://github.com/djmai"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class="text-primary">Miguel Martinez</a
            >
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mx-auto mb-16 max-w-3xl">
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <p class="mb-6 text-zinc-400">
          If you'd like to become a sponsor, please visit my
          <a href="/how-to-support" class="text-primary">How to Support</a> page.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>
